        <p>Pepp & Dolores operates peppanddolores.com in order to provide information about its restaurant as well as
          services to its customers. This Privacy Policy serves as the agreement between Pepp & Dolores and visitors
          to or users of the Website (collectively, “you” or “Users”), and governs our use of your personal
          information that we collect from you. The purpose of this Privacy Policy is to inform you how Pepp & Dolores
          may use that information, whether we disclose it to anyone, and the choices you have regarding your
          information.</p>

        <h2 class="space-md">Visitor Tracking</h2>
        <p>Pepp & Dolores places great importance on maintaining and protecting your private information. We do not
          require site registration to access the Website, in which case the only information collected is standard
