          particularly Users who have registered on the Website, will be used by Pepp & Dolores to provide you with
          requested information or services. Pepp & Dolores WILL NOT share your personal information with any other
          companies or individuals. Pepp & Dolores reserves the right to perform statistical analyses of User
          behavior in order to measure consumer interest in the various areas of our Website.</p>

        <h2 class="space-md">Registration and Volunteered Information</h2>
        <p>Portions of the Website require that Users give us contact information, such as a contact name, mailing
          address, phone number, and e-mail address. If you supply us with your e-mail address, you may receive
          periodic messages from Pepp & Dolores regarding our restaurant, promotions, and services, though you may
          opt out of receiving future mailings pursuant to the opt-out process set forth below.</p>

        <p>If you supply us with your postal address, you may receive periodic mailings from us with information
          on new promotions, services or upcoming events. If you do not wish to receive such mailings, please
          let us know by opting out pursuant to the opt-out process below.</p>

        <h2 class="space-md">Opt-Out Procedure</h2>
        <p>Pepp & Dolores will always provide you the opportunity to opt-out of receiving communications from
          us. You may request at any time not to receive future communications from us by choosing
          ‘unsubscribe’ from the most recent mailing you received. This assures that the email address to
          which we have been sending email is the one you are unsubscribing from our lists.</p>

        <p>If you have any issues regarding your email subscription with us, please
